---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 359
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=Non-Acting Action
By: Sri Ramana Maharshi
---
So long as egoity lasts prayatna (effort) is necessary. When egoity
ceases to be, actions become spontaneous. The ego acts in the presence
of the Self. He cannot exist without the Self.
